<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Codewithhamraz - Learn Coding 0 to 100% Free</title>
<meta name="description" content="Learn coding from 0 to 100% free with Humraz. HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Python tutorials in simple English.">
<style>
* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, sans-serif; }
body { background:#0f172a; color:#e2e8f0; line-height:1.7; }
header { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f97316,#ec4899); padding:80px 20px; text-align:center; }
header h1 { font-size:3rem; margin-bottom:15px; }
header p { font-size:1.3rem; color:#ffedd5; }
nav { background:#1e293b; padding:16px; display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:18px; flex-wrap:wrap; position:sticky; top:0; z-index:10; box-shadow:0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
nav a { color:#94a3b8; text-decoration:none; padding:10px 20px; border-radius:8px; font-weight:600; transition:0.3s; }
nav a:hover { background:#f97316; color:white; }
.container { max-width:1000px; margin:60px auto; padding:0 20px; }
.card { background:#1e293b; padding:35px; border-radius:16px; margin-bottom:35px; border-left:6px solid #f97316; }
h2 { color:#fb923c; margin-bottom:20px; font-size:2rem; }
h3 { color:#f472b6; margin:22px 0 12px 0; }
.level { display:inline-block; background:#22c55e; padding:6px 14px; border-radius:20px; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:14px; }
pre { background:#0b1120; padding:20px; border-radius:12px; overflow-x:auto; margin:20px 0; border:1px solid #334155; position:relative; }
code { color:#38bdf8; font-size:15px; }
.copy-btn { background:#f97316; border:none; color:white; padding:8px 16px; border-radius:7px; cursor:pointer; font-size:13px; position:absolute; top:12px; right:12px; font-weight:600; }
.copy-btn:hover { background:#ea580c; }
.grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(230px,1fr)); gap:22px; margin-top:30px; }
.box { background:#1e293b; padding:30px; border-radius:14px; text-align:center; border:2px solid #334155; transition:0.3s; }
.box:hover { border-color:#f97316; transform:translateY(-6px); }
footer { text-align:center; padding:45px 20px; color:#64748b; margin-top:70px; border-top:1px solid #334155; }
@media(max-width:600px) { header h1 { font-size:2.2rem; } .card { padding:22px; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
<h1>Codewithhamraz</h1>
<p>Learn Coding: 0 to 100% | Free Tutorials by Humraz</p>
