<section id="home" class="card">
<h2>🚀 Welcome to Codewithhamraz</h2>
<p><span class="level">Level 0</span> I teach coding in simple English + Hindi mix. No confusing words.</p>
<p><span class="level">Level 100%</span> Build projects, make portfolio, crack interviews.</p>
<p>Made by a 17-year-old for beginners like you. Let's start coding together!</p>

