<div class="box"><h3>📄 HTML</h3><p>Build website structure</p></div>
<div class="box"><h3>🎨 CSS</h3><p>Make it beautiful</p></div>
<div class="box"><h3>⚡ JavaScript</h3><p>Add magic & actions</p></div>
<div class="box"><h3>🐍 Python</h3><p>AI, Data, Backend</p></div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="html" class="card">
<h2>HTML Tutorial by Humraz</h2>
<h3><span class="level">Level 0</span> What is HTML?</h3>
<p>HTML = HyperText Markup Language. Think: HTML is the skeleton/bones of website. Without HTML, no website exists.</p>

<h3><span class="level">Level 1</span> Your First Code</h3>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Copy</button>
<pre><code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
  &lt;title&gt;My First Page - Codewithhamraz&lt;/title&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
  &lt;h1&gt;Hello! I am learning with Codewithhamraz&lt;/h1&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Coding is fun!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;</code></pre>
<p><b>Try this:</b> Save as `test.html` and open in browser. You will see your heading!</p>

<h3><span class="level">Level 100%</span> Project Challenge</h3>
<p>Make "About Me" page with your photo, name, 3 hobbies, and contact email. Share link with friends!</p>
</section>

<section id="css" class="card">
<h2>CSS Tutorial by Humraz</h2>
<h3><span class="level">Level 0</span> What is CSS?</h3>
<p>CSS = Cascading Style Sheets. If HTML is skeleton, CSS is skin, hair, clothes. CSS makes site colorful & modern.</p>

<h3><span class="level">Level 1</span> Color Your Text</h3>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Copy</button>
<pre><code>h1 {
  color: #f97316;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 45px;
  font-family: Arial;
}
p {
  background: #1e293b;
  padding: 15px;
  border-radius: 8px;
}</code></pre>
</section>

<section id="js" class="card">
<h2>JavaScript Tutorial by Humraz</h2>
<h3><span class="level">Level 0</span> What is JavaScript?</h3>
<p>JavaScript = Brain + Muscles. HTML=body, CSS=clothes, JS=brain. JS makes buttons work, forms submit, animations run.</p>

<h3><span class="level">Level 1</span> Button Click Magic</h3>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Copy</button>
<pre><code>&lt;button onclick="alert('Thanks for visiting Codewithhamraz!')"&gt;
  Click Me
&lt;/button&gt;</code></pre>
</section>

<section id="python" class="card">
<h2>Python Tutorial by Humraz</h2>
<h3><span class="level">Level 0</span> What is Python?</h3>
<p>Python = Easiest coding language. Reads like English. Used by Google, YouTube, Instagram, ChatGPT, AI.</p>

<h3><span class="level">Level 1</span> Your First Python Code</h3>
<button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Copy</button>
<pre><code>name = input("What is your name? ")
print("Welcome to Codewithhamraz, " + name + "!")
print("Let's learn coding together!")</code></pre>
</section>

<section id="about" class="card">
<h2>About Humraz</h2>
<p>Hi! I am Humraz, 17 years old. I started coding at 15. I know how confusing coding feels in the beginning.</p>
<p>That's why I made Codewithhamraz - to teach coding in the simplest way possible. 0 to 100% journey, step by step.</p>
<p>Follow me, learn with me, grow with me 🚀</p>
